      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRISON BREAK (1) was prominent throughout when winning in the fastest time of the card two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 4th and beaten 6 lengths at Sandown (29.59). Has ability and is a key runner. PAW IKE (7) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (34.83) at The Meadows latest. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings seven times from 13 attempts. Should be about the money. FAST FREDDY (8) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at 18 of 42 starts including 10 wins but missed the frame latest when eighth (30.22) over 515m at Sandown. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Will go close here with a clear run. JUMBUK SACHIN (2) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
